Old C/assembly guy who converted to Java/JEE in 2005.

I am engaged in back-end work, especially ReSTful based work. Other technologies include SQL, Hibernate, HTML/CSS, ant, Maven, Git. I do have some passing acquaintance with front-end technologies such as JSF and Facelets. Yesteryear: JSPs and servlets.
I use Eclipse as my IDE, but I prefer editing in Vim and using the Unix/Linux command line.
I've also dabbled successfully in Android.
I'm an Agile (Scrum) and test-driven development adept.
